      • setAmount

        public void setAmount(@NonNull
                      java.math.BigDecimal amount)
        Total amount of the transaction, including any Gratuity and or Taxes.

        If Tax is included, the tax amount should be set using setTaxAmount(BigDecimal)

        If Gratuity is included, the gratuity should be set using setGratuityAmount(BigDecimal)

        Parameters:
        amount - Total transaction amount to be authorized. This should include any gratuity and or taxes.
